name: Lines_007
description: Lines are simple. But Lines also tell a complex story. Lines narrate a journey from start to finish. StraightLines. JaggedLines. TimeLines. LifeLines. DeadLines. FlatLines. Are we not all Lines? Lines is a small collection of pieces constructed from a generative algorithm based on a few very simple rules. Start from somewhere, take a few turns, then terminate. 8000x8000 Originally created by [cmplx.tez 2022]
